organic.title: YWCA San Diego: Domestic Violence Services | Housing & Shelter
organic.snippet: YWCA of San Diego County provides comprehensive programs and services for people experiencing domestic violence and homelessness.

organic.title: Domestic Violence Services - YWCA of San Diego County
organic.snippet: YWCA of San Diego County (Becky's House) provides shelter, housing and support services for people experiencing domestic violence and abuse.

organic.title: Our History - YWCA San Diego County
organic.snippet: YWCA San Diego County has served women, families, and underserved people since 1908. YWCA opened the first domestic violence shelter in 1978.
